The paper deals with the problem of data association in multi-sensor systems, which is a common topic in robotics and control systems. Therefore, cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes decentralized methods, which fall under the scope of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper uses theoretical analysis and experimental evaluation, which suggests that it could also be relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning).
